command.text: M92 X80 Y80 Z80 A8.8889 ; Set steps per mm
M201 X2000 Y2000 Z2000 ; Set max accel
M203 X1000 Y1000 Z1000 ; Set max feedrate
M211 S0 ; Turn off soft safety limits
M204 P1000 T1000 ; set acell for homing
G0 Z33 F500 ; Move Z to park position
